        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This <em>+1 asp coil</em> is used by many trained Sisters of the Golden Erinys. It has a deep-red hue on each segment of the blade complemented by a pitch-black pommel. Death isn't the worst outcome for someone on the receiving end of its lashes.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate—Taste the Pain</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">f</span> (manipulate, visual)</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per hour</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> Your last action was a Strike with the crimson thorn that dealt damage to a creature</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> Attempt an Intimidation check to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Demoralize] the creature you dealt damage to with a +2 item bonus to the roll. You don't take any penalties to this check for not sharing a language.</p>"
